      <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn">
        <p>
		<lb n="1"/>kō-vicaiya
		<lb break="no" n="2"/>may<choice>
            <orig>i</orig>
            <reg>ē</reg>
          </choice>ntira-parumaṟku
		<lb n="3"/>mu-p-pattu naṅk-āvatu
	</p>
        <p>
		vāṇa-kō
		<lb break="no" n="4"/>-Araicaru maru-makkaḷ poṟṟokkai
		<lb break="no" n="5"/>-<choice>
            <orig>Ā</orig>
            <reg>yā</reg>
          </choice>r Iḷa-makaṉ karun-tēva-k-katti ta<choice>
            <orig>ṉ
		<lb break="no" n="6" style="text-align: right"/> ṉ</orig>
            <reg>ṉ</reg>
          </choice> erumai-p
		<lb break="no" n="7" style="text-align: right"/>-puṟattē vā
		<lb break="no" n="8" style="text-align: right"/>ṭi-p paṭṭā
		<lb break="no" n="9" style="text-align: right"/>ṉ kal
			</p>
      </div>
      <div type="apparatus">
        <listApp>
          <app loc="3">
            <lem>mu-p-pattu naṅk-āvatu</lem>
            <note><ptr target="bib:Deshpande1975_01"/> reads "fifty-fourth".</note>
          </app>
          <app loc="7">
            <lem>vā<lb break="no" n="8"/>ṭi-p paṭṭā<lb break="no" n="9"/>ṉ</lem>
            <rdg source="bib:Nakacami1972_01">vā<lb break="no" n="8"/>ṭi paṭṭā<lb break="no" n="9"/>ṉ</rdg>
          </app>
          <!--Display issue on line numbers: the 3 numbers appear-->
        </listApp>
      </div>
      <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation">
        <p n="1-3">Tirthy-fourth <supplied reason="subaudible">year</supplied> of the victorious king Mahendravarman<note>May<choice>
              <orig>i</orig>
              <reg>e</reg>
            </choice>ntiraparumaṉ <!--Display issue: space unneeded: May ¡i!--> the original Tamil.</note>.</p>
        <p n="3-9"><supplied reason="subaudible">This is</supplied> the stone <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> Karuntēvakkatti, the younger son <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> Poṟṟokkaiyār, the nephew of the royal Bāṇa king, he who fell and died <supplied reason="explanation">
            <foreign>vāṭi</foreign>
          </supplied> in the buffalo shed <supplied reason="explanation">
            <foreign>erumaippuṟam</foreign>
            <note>See <ptr target="bib:Deshpande1975_01"/><!--Display issue: siglum is not displayed-->for this meaning.</note>
          </supplied>
      		</p>
      </div>
      <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation" xml:lang="fra"></div>
      <div type="commentary">
        <p>See DHARMA_INSPallava00527 <!--update cross-ref--> for the label of the dog represented on the same slab.</p>
